{"type":"text","timestamp":1775872135218,"sessionID":"ses_285c6d36fffe6oZFwZp5oUO24e","part":{"id":"prt_d7a3a0f11001np4x9FIB8bhATl","messageID":"msg_d7a3a006a001Y6uTnq5sON3VY3","sessionID":"ses_285c6d36fffe6oZFwZp5oUO24e","type":"text","text":"Now I have a comprehensive view. Let me create a verification report:\n\n## AR-025 Verification Report\n\n### ✅ **Spec Requirements Met**\n\n#### Package Layout (design.md)\n| Path | Status | Notes |\n|------|--------|-------|\n| `pyproject.toml` | ✅ | Present with correct metadata |\n| `agentcube/__init__.py` | ✅ | Exports `__version__`, `app`, all runtimes |\n| `agentcube/cli/__init__.py` | ✅ | CLI subpackage marker |\n| `agentcube/cli/main.py` | ✅ | Typer app, all commands, helpers |\n| `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | ✅ | `MetadataOptions` dataclass |\n| `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | ✅ | Re-exports all runtimes |\n| `agentcube/runtime/*_runtime.py` | ✅ | All 5 runtime classes present |\n| `agentcube/services/__init__.py` | ✅ | Re-exports services + `AgentMetadata` |\n| `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | ✅ | `AgentMetadata`, `MetadataService` |\n| `agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | ✅ | `DockerService` |\n| `agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` | ✅ | `KubernetesProvider` |\n| `agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` | ✅ | `AgentCubeProvider` |\n| `agentcube/operations/__init__.py` | ✅ | Placeholder docstring |\n| `examples/hello-agent/main.py` | ✅ | Present |\n| `examples/math-agent/main.py` | ✅ | Present |\n\n#### Console Script Entry Point\n✅ **Correct:** `kubectl-agentcube = \"agentcube.cli.main:app\"`\n\n#### Setuptools Packages\n✅ **Correct:** All 6 packages listed including `agentcube.models`\n\n#### MetadataService & AgentMetadata\n✅ **All fields match spec:**\n- All 27 fields present with correct types and defaults\n- Validators: `language`, `build_mode`, `port` ✅\n- Methods: `load_metadata`, `save_metadata`, `update_metadata`, `validate_workspace` ✅\n\n#### MetadataOptions\n✅ **All fields match